==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Bub
<hw>Bub</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. 2d <er>Bubby</er>.]</ety> <def>A
young brother; a little boy; -- a familiar term of address of a small
boy.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bub</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Bub
<hw>Bub</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Abbrev. from
<er>Bubble</er>.]</ety> <def>To throw out in bubbles; to bubble.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Sackville.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bubale</ent>⟦br⟧
